item.description:
@wonderspring wrote:

I DID NOT MAKE THIS !
99.9% CREDITS TO WHO EVER MADE THIS ! I saw this for first time from Shoes on google. and 0.1% for me , transforming to non and writing here.

Create a new txt file and name it : Class20Sub1.java Inside that file add this code

public final class Class20Sub1 extends Class20 { public static void unpackConfigSub1(int j) { //Animations here ! } }

Open up Class20.java and under setAnimBase(j); add Class20Sub1.unpackConfigSub1(j);

Also, in class20.java, replace all “private” with “public” and if class20.java is a final class, get rid of the final.
